@token = YOUR_BEARER_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Search Services by Keyword (e.g., "plumb")
GET http://localhost:3000/services/search?q=plumb
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search Services by Keyword (e.g., "elect")
GET http://localhost:3000/services/search?q=elect
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search Workers offering a Specific Service ID (Sorted by Rating - default)
GET http://localhost:3000/workers/search?serviceId=YOUR_SERVICE_UUID_OR_INT_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search Workers Nearby (Filter by Distance & Sort by Distance)
GET http://localhost:3000/workers/search?serviceId=YOUR_SERVICE_UUID_OR_INT_HERE&lat=12.9716&lng=77.5946&maxDistance=15&sortBy=distance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search Workers (Filter by Rating & Price, Sorted by Price)
GET http://localhost:3000/workers/search?serviceId=YOUR_SERVICE_UUID_OR_INT_HERE&lat=12.9716&lng=77.5946&minRating=4.0&maxPrice=100&sortBy=price
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
